    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/c9bd2fcc16bbd173330ecd3c3bd538cf.poster.avif?t=1745248143\" width=614 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/c9bd2fcc16bbd173330ecd3c3bd538cf.webm?t=1745248143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/c9bd2fcc16bbd173330ecd3c3bd538cf.mp4?t=1745248143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Hexed Time</strong> is a hand-drawn point-and-click puzzle adventure set in a quaint medieval village. You play as Amelia, a seemingly ordinary grocer who lives among the village folk—though her simple life hides a powerful secret. Amelia is a witch, skilled in casting spells and brewing potions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a prophecy revealed through a crystal ball foretells a terrible fate for her dear friend, Amelia takes desperate action, trapping the day in a time loop. The loop will end only if her friend survives until midnight. However, she didn’t anticipate the arrival of the Inquisition, whose sole goal is to uncover and burn the witch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What will be your way out of the repeating day?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cast Spells and Brew Potions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a witch, Amelia has a range of magical abilities to help her manipulate the world around her. Cast spells and brew potions to solve puzzles, change outcomes, and shape the flow of the time to your liking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/6da316797d812e80eaed7560d3ab3cc8.poster.avif?t=1745248143\" width=614 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/6da316797d812e80eaed7560d3ab3cc8.webm?t=1745248143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/6da316797d812e80eaed7560d3ab3cc8.mp4?t=1745248143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Village</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village you inhabit is more than just a setting—it’s a dynamic world where your actions have consequences. Visit various locations, interact with villagers, and uncover hidden secrets as you explore. Discover how your decisions affect the lives of those around you and the path to breaking the loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/caf36825756fbc8e1418a331b664f27d.poster.avif?t=1745248143\" width=614 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/caf36825756fbc8e1418a331b664f27d.webm?t=1745248143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278590/extras/caf36825756fbc8e1418a331b664f27d.mp4?t=1745248143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reach Multiple Endings</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices throughout the game will determine the outcome. Will you find a way to save your friend and yourself, or will your magic and choices lead to an unexpected fate? Explore different paths and unlock up to three unique endings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Which one will you choose?</i></p>",
